Prerequisite:
pipenv (pip3 install pipenv)
vscode | REST Client extension by Huachao Mao

-----------------------------------------

1. git clone https://github.com/devnikhilmhatre/fynd_task
2. cd fynd-task
3. pipenv install
4. pipenv shell
5. python manage.py runserver (This command will start development server)
6. Open vscode and navigate to Api_Tests folder.
7. With http files in Api_Tests folder you can easily test all the available apis. 
   (Extension needed or can use Postman App)
8. Start with movies.http and hit http://127.0.0.1:8000/api-movies/ api first.
   (This will load all data from json to database)